WEBVTT

00:04:57.607 --> 00:05:03.983
I am talking about
the little insults and hurts

00:05:04.007 --> 00:05:08.663
that every woman has to put up
with on a daily basis all her life.

00:05:08.687 --> 00:05:13.423
Yet today, if we look at it,
there is hope for change.

00:05:13.447 --> 00:05:17.887
In every sector, women
are moving ahead rapidly

00:05:17.887 --> 00:05:20.887
and becoming more independent,

00:05:20.887 --> 00:05:27.887
and men will have to partner with them
because only then is true love possible.